data.description: Stunning house in Lorson Ranch!!!! Won't last long! This stunning Lorson Ranch home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a 2 car garage. This open floor concept floor plan boasts hardwood floor entry, kitchen and dining area. Stainless steel appliances and birch cabinets with crown molding. Recessed lighting in kitchen and ceiling fans in living room & master bedroom. Open floor plan, two-story entryway and conveniently located laundry room close to all 3 bedrooms. Fully fenced in backyard with a cement patio great for entertaining and beautiful mountain views. This home is move in ready.
